</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></CodeDemo><h5 id="曲线命令" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#曲线命令" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 曲线命令</h5>
<h6 id="q-quadratic-bezier-curve-to" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#q-quadratic-bezier-curve-to" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Q（Quadratic Bezier Curve to）</h6>
<p><code v-pre>Q</code>命令可以用来绘制一条<code v-pre>二次贝塞尔曲线</code>，<code v-pre>二次贝塞尔曲线</code>需要一个<code v-pre>控制点</code>，用来确定<code v-pre>起点</code>和<code v-pre>终点</code>的<code v-pre>曲线斜率</code>。</p>
<p><strong>语法：</strong> Q x1 y1, x y 或者 q x1 y1, x y</p>
<p><strong>参数：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>x、y为<code v-pre>终点位置</code></li>
<li>x1、y1为<code v-pre>控制点</code></li>
</ul>

<CodeDemo id="code-demo-673" type="vue" code="eJxNjsEKwjAMhl8lxAdopgxhVN/Ag/deBkvXYu2KjVMR393oLssp+fh+/rxxvjN2aIWvJfXCR5cBbJ1HeMRBwsHhjqg8HULgOAZRsF3A31S39BJgUH5qCRoiOEOzb0Et0OiPaNjHlFTJU2a9qrwS61nlNl24g433pOPQLPVG+3WzZvUVfr5jGTNw">
<div class="language-vue line-numbers-mode" data-ext="vue"><pre v-pre class="language-vue"><code><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>template</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>
